  "body": "<p>Things are busy over here as usual - I updated the Upcoming Events on the side ----&gt; and there's even some more in the works. Thank you so much for all your sweet words about Stitched! As you may remember, I was on HSN for the first time back in March. It turns out another big HSN craft event is happening next week and unfortunately with everything going on here, I cannot make it. Though I am sad to not be in Florida for HSN this time around, I am SO grateful to have the amazing <a href=\"http://www.lisabearnson.com/2014/10/01/giveaway-day-3-amy-tangerine-plus-one/\">Lisa Bearnson</a> there featuring some Amy Tangerine Plus One products. She's a total pro at what she does and I'm excited to set my DVR to watch her do her magic and unleash some amazing deals - everything is 25% to 40% off! You can purchase them now or while she's featuring them at 4am EST on Tuesday, October 7. 1. <a href=\"http://www.hsn.com/shop/amy-tangerine/12206?rid=3635&amp;query=amy%20tangerine&amp;isSuggested=False&amp;\">Amy Tangerine Embroidery Stencil Kit</a>: This kit is 25% off the HSN price! Check it out <a href=\"http://www.hsn.com/shop/amy-tangerine/12206?rid=3635&amp;query=amy%20tangerine&amp;isSuggested=False&amp;\">here</a>–only $14.95!</p><p>2. <a href=\"http://www.hsn.com/products/amy-tangerine-plus-one-papercrafting-kit/7407018\">Plus One Paper Crafting Kit:</a> This kit has it all–48 sheets of paper, 283 accents and phrases, 720 letters and numbers stickers, 168 foam letter stickers, rub-ons, sticker roll and die-cut shapes. Whew! And wait ’til you see the price: <a href=\"http://http//www.hsn.com/products/amy-tangerine-plus-one-papercrafting-kit/7407018\">$16.95</a>! This is 40% off the already low HSN price!</p><p>3. <a href=\"http://www.hsn.com/products/amy-tangerine-stamp-and-marker-set/7407044\">Amy Tangerine Stamp and Marker Set</a>. Wow–this is on sale for <a href=\"http://www.hsn.com/products/amy-tangerine-stamp-and-marker-set/7407044\">$16.95</a> (40% off the HSN price). There are 22 acrylic stamps, a roller date stamp and rotary phrase stamp, plus five slick writers.</p><p><a href=\"http://www.lisabearnson.com/2014/10/01/giveaway-day-3-amy-tangerine-plus-one/\">Lisa</a> and I are both giving away an Amy Tangerine Scrapbook kit - winners will be announced Monday, October 6th. The sign up is at the bottom of this post. Good luck!</p><p>Here's a handful of gorgeous projects featuring my Plus One collection:</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598437966353-QYY7JPR30E15WIOH1OTM/2a-39c8e02e58a0faf721a0080a7b7cd16b-600x399.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Party Set-Up by <a href=\"http://www.thetomkatstudio.com/amytangerine/\">The Tomkat Studio</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598437981461-WQ59ZT9V9YWH32O8HLB0/2b-Amy-Tangerine-Plus-One-11-578x838-413x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Gift Wrap Ideas by <a href=\"http://pagingsupermom.com/2014/03/amy-tangerine-plus-one/\">Paging Super Mom</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598437997369-7OM2AEV1GX509YKKYVAP/2c-Picture-Frame-Photo-Display-with-Amy-Tangerine-600x576.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Photo Display by <a href=\"http://www.mom4real.com/2014/03/make-a-photo-display-with-amy-tangerine.html\">Mom 4 Real</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598438014675-QU2H3QVYFUNQBVFALEZ1/image-asset.png\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Stitched Art by <a href=\"http://www.myfabulesslife.com/2014/03/spring-decorating-ideas.html\">My Fabuless Life</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598438038955-XL60XOEBY7RPIEECKHQ9/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Upcycled Frame by <a href=\"http://www.kimberlykalil.com/2014/03/crafting-upcycled-frame-amy-tangerines-plus-one/\">Kimberly Kalil</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598438056636-6JSYZHL20IE6XMUT9SVC/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Welcome to the Neighborhood Gift by <a href=\"http://www.thehappyscraps.com/2014/03/welcome-to-neighborhood-gift.html\">The Happy Scraps</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598438080758-OX19PKVKNRWVIJHWUNDK/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Countdown Calendar by<a href=\"http://www.attagirlsays.com/2014/03/21/calendar-countdown-craft/\"> Atta Girl Says</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598438103275-NQ7OS7CN0RSPY74ES2R1/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Summer To-Do List by <a href=\"http://www.triedandtrueblog.com/summer-to-do-list/\">Tried &amp; True</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598438121487-47YK40LID7JW8M6T31IN/2i-Doll-House-9-526x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Dollhouse Remodel by <a href=\"http://www.howtogal.com/2014/03/dollhouse-remodel-with-scrapbook-paper.html\">How To Gal</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598438141722-7RPRJ41JD1HOUIVPJ6VX/2j-IMG_4324-600x399.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Embroidered Banner by <a href=\"http://www.welcometothemousehouse.com/2014/03/create-embroidered-banner-amy-tangerine.html\">Welcome to the Mouse House</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598438164666-71N8RBUU0EKP5LEXACKQ/2k-amy-tangerine-embroidered-map-after2-600x398.png\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Embroidered Map by <a href=\"http://www.brendabirddesigns.com/embroidered-map-amy-tangerine-plus-one-collection/\">From Me, With Love</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>In case you missed any of the previous Plus One project posts, here's Part One, Part Two, Part Three and Part Four!</p><p><a href=\"http://www.rafflecopter.com/rafl/display/e549cfae9/\">a Rafflecopter giveaway</a></p><p>Good luck!</p>"
